server
---------
incoming events:
  actions do security checks
  model just executes what action pass (no more checks!)

outoging events:
 * world creates the basic results
 * actions serialize them for each askins/ sending client

 * runs one world with islands
 * pushes events to clients

client
--------
 * only visualization
 * & command

each client can pick one island.

maybe add FLAGS

events
---------
unit server -> client
   add
   remove
   move
   setPath
args: unitIdx, type, islandIdx, cell

unit client -> server
   add
   setPath (moveableUnit)
args: type, islandIdx, cell

displayed values server -> client
   goldcount
   month
   census.total
   census.houseless
   census.unhappy
args: name, value
